data.description: Beautifully maintained, updated townhome located in a sought-after Olde Royal Park subdivision in Kennesaw! This townhome lives like a single-family home, with no common walls and is connected by its very own storage room. The bright and open floor plan features new Luxury Vinyl Plank flooring throughout the entire home! As you step inside, you're greeted by a warm and inviting formal living/dining room combo that can also be used as a home office or flex space. The eat-in kitchen boasts stainless steel appliances, ample cabinetry and plenty of counter space with a breakfast area overlooking the spacious two-story family room with gas fireplace. The sliding glass door off the kitchen opens to the private fenced backyard with turf and a shaded patio. Upstairs, you'll find the spacious primary bedroom featuring a private ensuite bathroom with dual vanities, soaking tub and standing shower along with a large, walk-in closet. Two additional bedrooms share a sizable secondary bathroom. Located in a desirable community with low monthly HOA fees and close to shopping, restaurants, Kennesaw State University, I-75/575 and easy access to the Express Lanes (Peach Pass).
